---
source: clash/tests/cli_help_snapshots.rs
assertion_line: 88
expression: "get_subcommand_help(\"statusline\")"
---
Display clash status in the Claude Code status line

Usage: statusline <COMMAND>

Commands:
  render     Render status line (reads JSON from stdin, prints formatted output)
  install    Install the status line into Claude Code settings
  uninstall  Remove the status line from Claude Code settings
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
